  "texts": [
    "Through a series of experiments involving multiple advanced LLMs, we have showcased their remarkable capabilities in mastering urban planning knowledge.",
    "However, there remains substantial untapped potential to fully leverage LLMs to enhance the productivity of human practitioners in this field.",
    "We envision that our findings will foster interdisciplinary collaboration between human planners and AI practitioners, paving the way for further exploration and the application of LLMs in influential real-world urban planning scenarios.",
    "Moving forward, our future work includes expanding both UrbanPlanBench and UrbanPlanText to incorporate multi-linguistic urban planning materials, thereby enabling broader use cases of the benchmark and dataset.",
    "Additionally, we aim to extend UrbanPlanBench into a multi-modal benchmark, integrating both imagery of urban plans and their corresponding descriptive text, further enriching the evaluation capabilities of LLMs in urban planning contexts."
